Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:26.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんで… うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:32.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんで わからねえんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:40.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,もうじき お前の体は…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:43.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸に とられちまうんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:50.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サスケ)そうなったら そうなっただ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.31,0:00:57.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,子供のままだな… ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:01:01.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレにとっては 復讐がすべてだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:05.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,復讐さえ叶えば\Nオレがどうなろうが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:09.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,この世がどうなろうが\N知ったことじゃない…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:12.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,はっきり言うとだ…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:17.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,イタチは 今のオレでも\N大蛇丸でも倒せない。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:22.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが 大蛇丸に\Nオレの体を差し出すことで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:26.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,それを成し得る力を\N手にできるなら…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:30.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,こんな命 いくらでもくれてやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:34.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)話は終わりだ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:40.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)ナルトとサクラ… キミたちの手前➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:43.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,彼に手荒なマネは\Nしたくなかったが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:46.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,悪いが… もう本気でやるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)ヤマト隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:50.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,本気で って…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:55.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)大蛇丸同様\N里抜けした者を➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:58.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,野放しにしとく\Nわけにもいかないしね。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:03.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)どんな手を使ってでも\N彼を木ノ葉に連行する。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:07.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:10.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前たちは もういい…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,終わりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:29.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:33.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,(大蛇丸)その術は\Nやめておきなさい… サスケ君。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,放せ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カブト)こらこら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:46.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸様に向かって\Nまたそんな口の利き方を…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:57.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,やめる理由はない…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:05:01.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,今の暁の動きを\Nキミも知ってるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カブト)この木ノ葉の人たちには➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:10.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,暁を始末しておいて\Nもらいたいんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:14.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,１人でも多くね…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:17.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,他の暁に ジャマされると➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:20.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,キミの復讐も\Nうまくいかなくなるだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:24.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,情けない理由だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:29.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,復讐の可能性を\N１％でも上げるためだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:32.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,行くわよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:25.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,《また…\Nまた止められなかった…》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:32.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,《オレは… よえぇ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:07.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)泣いたって… 泣いたって\Nサスケ君は 帰ってこないでしょ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:17.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,私も いる。\N私だって 一緒に強くなる！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:29.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サイ)時間… あと半年近くは\Nあるんだよね。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:33.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サイ)２人より ３人のほうが\Nいいに決まってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:37.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,それに ボクは 結構 強いからね。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:58.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,ありがとう。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,さて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:08.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,《これからだな…》
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:34.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,(トントン)ブヒッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,(綱手)そうか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:48.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,はぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:05.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カカシ)なんですって!?\Nナルトたちが サスケと？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,(自来也)うん。\Nしかし➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:10.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,アイツらの本来の任務は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:14.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,そう あやつらの任務は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:18.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリが大蛇丸のもとに送り込んだ\Nスパイを拘束➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉に連れ帰ること。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:25.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸やサスケの情報を\N得るためにもな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:29.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが サソリのスパイ 薬師 カブトは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:33.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸によって すでに\Nサソリの術を解かれておった。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:35.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして 大蛇丸は この機に➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:39.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,サソリを亡き者に\Nしようとしていたらしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:43.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,本物のサソリが すでに\N死んでいることを知らずにのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:49.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸と接触した ナルトは\N感情を抑えきれなくなり 暴走。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:56.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトは ついに ４本目の尾まで出し\N暴れまくった。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:11:00.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,さしもの大蛇丸も\N九尾状態のナルトと やりあって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:04.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,限界を迎えたのじゃろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:08.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヤマトが ナルトを押さえ込む間に\N姿を消そうとしたようだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:12.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,しかし ヤマトの分身が 密かに追跡。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:19.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,ついに 大蛇丸のアジトを突き止め\N内部に進入。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:24.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,そこで サスケと遭遇し\N戦闘になったらしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,それで どうなったんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:40.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケは\N相当 力をつけとったらしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:44.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,(自来也)ナルトは\Nまるで 歯が立たんかったそうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:47.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,はぁ… そうですか。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,まぁ そう落ち込むな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトは 九尾化のダメージで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:54.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,十分に\N力を出せんかったようだし➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,それに…。\Nいえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:59.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,それほど 落ち込んでるわけじゃ\Nないですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:03.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,現時点では サスケのほうが上だと\N思ってましたし➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,それに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:09.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カカシ)\Nサスケとの差を自覚したことで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:12.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,これからの修業にも\N気合が入る。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:14.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,でしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:17.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,フン だのう。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:20.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,まぁ 今回は\N無事に帰ってきただけで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:22.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,よしとしましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:35.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ホムラ)ナルトが 無事に帰ってきたのは\N幸運じゃったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:40.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,(コハル)しかし 任務には\N不測の事態がつきものとはいえ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:44.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,まさか 大蛇丸と\Nやりあうことになるとは。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,(コハル)こういうことがあるから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:50.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルトは 里に とどめておいたほうが\Nよいのに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:56.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ホムラ)あの頑固者が 簡単に\N意見を曲げるとは思えんしな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:58.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,う～ん…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:05.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,はぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,…で？\Nオレたちは あきらめねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:26.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,フッ では お前たちには\Nすぐ 次の任務を言い渡す。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:29.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,おって連絡があるまで\N自宅待機。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:31.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,おう！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:43.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,なぁ サクラちゃん\Nこのまま ２人でデートしようか。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:47.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,アンタ たった今 綱手様に\N言われたこと 忘れたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:49.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,あ？ 何だっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:54.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,私たち カカシ班は 次の任務が\N決まるまで 自宅待機でしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:57.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,あぁ ちょっとだけなら\Nばれねえってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)デートしたいなら\N１人ですれば？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや １人じゃできねえってばよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:04.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,(綱手)ところで サイの動きは？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:07.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,はい 綱手様が\N心配されていたとおり➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:11.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,ダンゾウから\N特別任務を与えられていました。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,特別任務？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:15.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,《シズネ : やはり…》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:19.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)サイは ダンゾウの指示で\N暗部として 任務をこなしつつ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:21.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉に対する危険人物の➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:25.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,諜報活動 および 処理に\N当たっていたようです。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:30.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,サイが 今回\Nボクたち カカシ班に合流した目的は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:34.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉が もっとも注意すべき人物\N大蛇丸…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:39.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,その大蛇丸の 新たなる肉体\Nサスケを葬ることだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.33,japanese,,0,0,0,,えっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:47.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,フン… 食えない男だと\N思っていたが。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:52.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,方法は 武闘派路線の\N主導者だけあって 強引だが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:56.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉を思う気持は\Nひとつということか。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,それは ダンゾウのことを\Nおっしゃっているのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:02.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,ん？ そうだが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:07.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,では 結論は これをご覧に\Nなってからにしてもらえますか。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:13.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,(綱手)これは？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:17.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,ダンゾウが 大蛇丸との接触を\N円滑に進めるために➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:21.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,サイに持たせた\N大蛇丸への手土産です。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:28.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,こ… これは！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:32.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,暗部の構成員リスト！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:34.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,《クソ… ダンゾウのヤツ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:39.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,極秘ファイルの中から\Nリストを どうやって手に入れた!?》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:42.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの 綱手様…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:46.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,シズネ！ 極秘ファイル倉庫への\N警備の強化 および➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,ファイルの解読暗号の変更を急げ！\Nあ… はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:51.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,今すぐだ！\Nあひぃ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:58.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,アハハハハ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:05.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,クソ！ あのタヌキじじい…\Nどこまでいっても 食えないヤツだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:10.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,(綱手)大蛇丸 暁と\N里の外が騒がしいってときに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:15.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,里内部のごたごたまで\N考えなきゃならんとは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:21.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,これでは 先ほどの サイの申し入れ\N慎重に考えざるをえんな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:24.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,それでしたら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,ん…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:47.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ダンゾウ)特別任務をしくじるとは…。\Nお前らしくないな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サイ)ひとつ お願いがございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:55.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ダンゾウ)願い… だと？\N(サイ)はい。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:57.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,この名のまま しばらく➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:17:01.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,カカシ班に身を置かせては\Nいただけないでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:09.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,《この笑い顔は…》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:15.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ダンゾウ)その話なら\N綱手からも受けている。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.19,0:17:17.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,しかし… わかっているな？ サイ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:24.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,感情は 憎しみを作り出す。 そして\N憎しみは 戦いを作り出すものだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:32.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,((兄との憎しみっていう\Nつながりがな))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:37.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サイ)そうかもしれませんね。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:41.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,《でも…》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:47.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,((アイツは 誰よりも オレのことを\N認めてくれた１人だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:51.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケは オレの友達だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:56.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,(やっとできた 大切なつながりだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:43.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,((お前 「仲間」って言葉\N知ってっか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:48.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,(もちろん 知ってますが…\Nそれが 何か？))
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:14.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,≪お～い サイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:26.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,次の任務の\N打ち合わせだってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:46.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,≪早くしろってばよ！\N(サイ)あぁ 今 行くよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:27.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,たっだいま…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,フゥ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.39,0:21:42.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カカシ)はいは～い！ 写真撮るから\Nみんな ちゃんとして。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:44.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんで オレ様が コイツなんかと➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:46.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,一緒に写らなきゃ\Nいけねえんだってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:49.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,こっちのセリフだ うすらトンカチ！\Nなっ… なんだとぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:52.20,japanese,,0,0,0,,まぁまぁ… これ 決まりだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:55.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,でも 嬉しいなぁ！ サスケ君と\N一緒に写れるなんて！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:59.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレも！ オレも！ サクラちゃんと\N写れて 超嬉しいってば！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:01.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,先生… ナルトは外してください。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:03.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,ガ～ン… そんなぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:05.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,フン…。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:07.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,笑うな！\Nあん？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:10.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カカシ)いい加減にしろ ２人とも。\N写真屋さんも困ってるでしょ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:14.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カカシ)ほら… これ 残るんだから\N笑って 笑って！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:16.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カカシ)はい！ じゃあ\Nお願いしま～す！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:24.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.83,0:00:31.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:43.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, Orochimaru's going\Nto take your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.87,0:00:50.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If it happens, it happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:57.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a kid, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:01.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge is everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:04.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can carry out my revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:08.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,it's no concern of mine\Nwhat happens to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:09.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,or to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.87,0:01:17.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Put simply, neither I nor Orochimaru\Ncan defeat Itachi right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:22.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I can obtain the power\Nto accomplish that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:27.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,by giving my body to Orochimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:30.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll give him as much of\Nthis life of mine as he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:16.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Title\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:33.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The talking's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto and Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:43.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to do anything rough\Nin front of you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm going to get serious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:50.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, serious...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just let those
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:58.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,who left the village in the same way\Nas Orochimaru run loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:03.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll do whatever I have to do\Nto haul Sasuke back to the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:06.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hidden Leaf, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:09.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:28.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:33.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother with that Jutsu, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:35.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:40.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey-hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:46.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to\NLord Orochimaru like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:56.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no reason to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:01.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what the Akatsuki\Nare up to, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We want these guys from\Nthe Hidden Leaf
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:09.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,to take care of the Akatsuki for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,As many of them as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:17.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Your revenge won't turn out well
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,if the other Akatsuki\Nget in the way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pathetic reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:28.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It should increase your chances of revenge,\Neven if only by one percent...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:30.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:20.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again...I couldn't stop him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:32.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm...totally weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:06.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Crying won't bring Sasuke back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:17.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here! I'll get stronger with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:28.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got...\Nclose to six months left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:33.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes without saying that three\Nare better than two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm pretty strong myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:04.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:07.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is just the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:35.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hidden Leaf Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:03.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto and the others fought Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:06.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:10.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But, their original mission was to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:19.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, their mission was to capture\Nthe spy Sasori sent to Orochimaru
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and bring him back to the Hidden Leaf,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:25.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and to get information about Orochimaru\Nand Sasuke as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:29.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sasori's spy, Kabuto Yakushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:33.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,already had Sasori's Jutsu\Nbroken by Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:39.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems Orochimaru tried to use\Nthis opportunity to kill Sasori,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:43.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,not knowing that the real Sasori\Nwas already dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto made contact with Orochimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:48.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,became unable to\Ncontrol his emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:49.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and ran amuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:55.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto eventually\Nreleased his fourth tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:56.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and went wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:01.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru did battle\Nwith the Nine-Tails Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even he probably reached his limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:06.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Stabilize\N\N\N\N\NIt seems he tried to disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,while Yamato was attempting\Nto control Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Yamato's clone secretly\Npursued Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:18.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, they found Orochimaru's hideout\Nand made their way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:23.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it seems they encountered Sasuke\Nand a battle ensued.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So...then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:40.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Sasuke has become\Nsignificantly more powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:43.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear Naruto didn't stand\Na chance against him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't get so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:52.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears Naruto wasn't able\Nto show his full power
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,because of damage from\Nthe Nine-Tails Cloak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:56.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:59.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm not all that depressed,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:03.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured Sasuke would be stronger\Nat this point in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:05.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Naruto will be more fired up\Nfor future training
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,after having realized the difference\Nbetween Sasuke and himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:17.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:22.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess we should be happy\Nthey made it back safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:35.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fortunate that Naruto\Nwas able to make it back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:40.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,However, although unexpected situations\Nare an inevitable part of missions...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:44.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought he would end up\Ndoing battle with Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And here, it's best to keep Naruto\Nin the village
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,because things like this\Nend up happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:56.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that hard-head\Nwould depart from his opinions so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:09.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:12.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:26.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I will issue\Nyour next mission immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by at home until I contact you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:30.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:43.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sakura.\NLet's go on a date together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:47.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten what Lady Tsunade\Nsaid just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:49.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What'd she say again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:51.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to stand by at home
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:54.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,until Team Kakashi's next mission\Nhas been determined, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What? She won't find out if\Nwe just go out for a little while!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go by yourself\Nif you want to go out on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to\Ngo on a date by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what about Sai's activity?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:08.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You were right\Nto be concerned, Lady Tsunade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Danzo gave him a special mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,A special mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:14.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Sai was put in charge\Nof undercover work,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:20.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,dealing with potential risks\Nto the Hidden Leaf
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:23.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,while carrying out his mission as
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,an Anbu Black Ops member\Nunder Danzo's direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:30.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai's purpose for joining us in\NTeam Kakashi was to bury Sasuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:34.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,who is to become the new vessel\Nfor Orochimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:39.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,the individual of most concern\Nto the Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured he was a crafty guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:50.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,As would be expected of the leader\Nof a hard-line military faction,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:51.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,his actions are strong-armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:55.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But our protective feelings\Nfor the Hidden Leaf are the same, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:59.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about Danzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:07.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then could you hold off on\Nyour conclusions until you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:13.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:17.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Danzo gave this to Sai as\Na gift for Orochimaru
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:21.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,in order for the contact with Orochimaru\Nto proceed smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a list of Anbu Black Ops members!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:35.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it! That jerk, Danzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:39.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How did he get the list from\N{\i1}the classified files...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:42.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...Lady Tsunade...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:45.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizune! Tighten security at\Nthe classified files storehouse
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and change the deciphering codes\Nfor the files. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:49.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:50.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! That sly old dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:04.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always the crafty one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:07.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,At a time when the outside\Nof the village
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:10.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,is in an uproar with Orochimaru\Nand the Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:13.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd have to be concerned\Nabout trouble {\i1}inside{\i0}  the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:20.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll be forced to consider Sai's\Nearlier proposal with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:22.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:44.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd fail\Nthe special mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:47.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very unlike you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,A favor, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:55.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:17:00.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you keep me in Team Kakashi\Nunder this name for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:09.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That smile on his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:14.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already taken that up\Nwith Tsunade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:20.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But you understand that emotions\Ncreate hate, don't you, Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:24.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And hate creates battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:32.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bonds of hatred with\N{\i1}my older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:37.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:39.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:45.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the person who acknowledged\N{\i1}me more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:51.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sasuke is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.43,english,,0000,0000,0000